  <description><![CDATA[<p>This stylish hotel has some of the best sea views of any hotel in Italy. Set into the cliffside, all bedrooms have balconies facing the sea and there are 180 degree views of the Bay of Naples all the way to Mount Vesuvius. Yet, the centre of Sorrento is just a 15 minute walk away. The bedrooms have chic decor and the superior rooms have spacious terraces with sunbeds.</p>]]></description>
